Package: steveproj
Type: Package
Title: Steve's Academic R Projects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Steven V. Miller
Maintainer: Steven V. Miller <steven.v.miller@gmail.com>
Description: This is a one-function suite and skeleton project directory to help you
    start and manage R projects with an eye toward producing an academic project (to 
    culminate in an academic paper). This package will lean on "R Markdown" and "Make".
BugReports: https://github.com/svmiller/steveproj/issues
URL: http://svmiller.com/steveproj/
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
